spfft
------------------------------------------
A 3D FFT library for sparse frequency domain data written in C++ with support
for MPI, OpenMP, CUDA and ROCm.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.0-1
  libfftw3-devel-3.3.10-1
  libfftw3_3-3.3.10-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libgomp1-12.4.0-3
  libspfft-devel-1.1.1-1bl1
  libspfft1-1.1.1-1bl1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-fortran-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libfftw3-devel-3.3.10-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/eth-cscs/SpFFT

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/eth-cscs/SpFFT/archive/refs/tags/v1.1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack spfft-1.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./spfft-1.1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/spfft-1.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/spfft-1.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libspfft1-1.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libspfft-devel-1.1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

